subs.text: You can invent and evolve a new sport if you have all the elements. If you've got enough players, a venue, journalists, fans. If you want to change the rules, you don't need to get anyone's approval, you just need a vision, and you have to do the work.

subs.text: That's how I got blogging going. I had tools for writing, and reading, and I generated feeds myself because I am a writer.
